{"tid":2027711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡安法今日殺唔死我地 我地就要殺死惡安法","createTime":"2020-05-21T13:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T09:46:53.000Z","uid":199893,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"bd618ffed7afff1706532f883933f5a57eaff4de","tid":2027711,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"今日你殺我唔死仲畀咗七日我<br />\n你準備仆街死啦中共<br />\n<br />\n相信大家好清楚單憑一個人係不足以扭轉時局<br />\n但我地係一班人<br />\n冇時間灰啦 一齊攜手反擊啦仲諗<br />\n<br />\n1. 陣地戰冇用啦 班撚屌係北京 我地喺香港<br />\n<br />\n2. 惡安法有少少聲就已經嚇到股市又有變動<br />\n唔係唔喺呢邊落手呀？<br />\n惡安法一定會嚴重打擊香港社經地位<br />\n相信外國唔係有好多人關注緊呢件事<br />\n我地不妨再次將「惡安法」呢個地區/國家政策變成<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際政策</span></span><br />\n再借用國際力量要脅中共"},{"pid":"bea354f9a70b55c5837a9c9a96b15f39ed39b009","tid":2027711,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多 留得七日畀我諗<br />\n畀我打 畀我還拖 唔係唔打呀"},{"pid":"e026b373e7439fddce857cf39cc4a87a1154d473","tid":2027711,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"屌 佢有腹肌啫<br />\n但佢舊腹肌冇撚用架<br />\n佢打贏我唔係因為舊腹肌"},{"pid":"30e84617e9297e741317de585d8832c644945e44","tid":2027711,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:21:33.000Z","msg":"國際戰線呀"},{"pid":"967f438aeb5d6aef797b20cf82909783b10b5bfb","tid":2027711,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"認真看待呀"},{"pid":"fa6b499c0e59a0a5b8830844b4b1c576ca394075","tid":2027711,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:22:55.000Z","msg":"同埋 唔好太依賴連登"},{"pid":"30ebc9a1f489e58f966bdcfebfba19b035bcefd2","tid":2027711,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:23:26.000Z","msg":"連登早已淪陷"},{"pid":"b719a5b40757bb19b98478f2a1c4148d92c6b7f1","tid":2027711,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy